    "Metadata": {
        "Id": "7410b7c0-9bae-48c9-9e06-6167a1ee235b",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "门多萨清除行动  Mendoza Cleanup",
        "Location": "LOCATION_ELEGANT_LLAMA",
        "PublicId": "131565897932",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/elegant/scene_llama.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 58dba19f-aa5b-4671-b4be-dbb4ebbd9a5b).Image",
        "Description": "47，门多萨的耶茨酒庄此刻正有一场不对外公开的私下会面。到场的四人并非普通宾客，而是神意秘会在南美片区的中层执行者，正借着这场酒会密谋跨境非法交易。你需顺势将他们处理掉，用场地制造合理意外，不留任何与 ICA 相关的痕迹。\r47, a private gathering is underway at Viñedo Yates, Mendoza. The four targets are Providence mid-level operatives in South America, plotting illegal cross-border trades under the cover of the wine event. Eliminate them with plausible accidents and leave no ICA trace.",
